<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.1">
<l>aṟiva tariyā ṉaṉaittulaku muṭaiyā ṉeṉṉai yāḷuṭaiyāṉ</l>
<l>kuṟiya māṇi yuruvāya kūttaṉ maṉṉi yamarumiṭam</l>
<l>naṟiya malarmēl curumpārkka veḻilār maññai naṭamāṭa</l>
<l>poṟikoḷ ciṟaivaṇ ṭicaipāṭum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where eternally rests the performer</l>
<l rend="indent">in the form of a dwarf brahmacarya,</l>
<l>The one who comprehending is difficult,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who possesses the whole world,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who has accepted me as a servant,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtaṅkuṭi where bees with wings with spots sing melodies,</l>
<l>As drones hum on fragrant blossoms, while graceful peacocks</l>
<l rend="indent">perform their dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
